Conditional Operator (?:) 條件運算子

?: 可以代替if...else statement (this can make your code sorter and clearer)

conditional operator 是 c++ 唯一的ternary operator(三元運算，接受三個運算元)

operands and the ?: symbol from a conditional expression:

cout << (studentGrade >= 60 ? "Passed" : "Failed");

在？之間，如果條件為真，則：
條件為假，則：右側的操作數是條件表示式的值


